{"tid":103044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疑阻路遭淋黑油　私家車變身「粉紅斑馬」","createTime":"2017-02-01T05:12:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-01T06:05:57.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6e09d5c102da0b04285828e44b91c92a5e9a171d","tid":103044,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:12:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170201/bkn-20170201093042737-0201_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170201%2Fbkn-20170201093042737-0201_00822_001.html&d=IyvsStEAH7GPomOhwpmPFZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=505ef19a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170201/bkn-20170201093042737-0201_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170201/photo/bkn-20170201093042737-0201_00822_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170201%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170201093042737-0201_00822_001_01p.jpg&h=7eb64f03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n私家車疑阻路遭淋黑油。（黃永健攝）<br />\n<br />\n荃灣關門口村再有私家車被淋油。早上7時許，有村民行發現一輛停泊在村內掘頭路的粉紅色私家車，左邊車身遭人淋潑黑油，儼如粉紅斑馬。由於該車停泊位置為樓梯口，擋住村內3條通道，不排除因此遭破壞。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170201/photo/bkn-20170201093042737-0201_00822_001_02p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170201%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170201093042737-0201_00822_001_02p.jpg&h=473b73c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n私家車停在村內掘頭路。（網民Chongchong圖片）<br />\n<br />\n去年11月26日早上8時許，一輛同樣停泊在村內掘頭路的七人車，亦遭人淋潑紅油，前後擋風玻璃及車頂均「中招」，警方列刑事毀壞案處理。"},{"pid":"4c173079c89726ff53f59a743c18060f94dd447d","tid":103044,"uid":20102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:13:32.000Z","msg":"幾有美感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2395276c7b4c7e3a9c8f132c1c45a808c659d295","tid":103044,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi